                    "line_text": "La nuée au vent flotte ainsi qu'une toison ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Et les vagues de sable, emplissant l'horizon,",
